    "Override user interface idiom to iPadOS, so you could use all iPadOS multitasking features on iPhone. Gives you the same capabilities as TrollPad, but may cause some issues.\nPLEASE DO NOT TURN OFF SHOW DOCK IN STAGE MANAGER OTHERWISE YOUR PHONE WILL BOOTLOOP WHEN ROTATING TO LANDSCAPE.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "将用户界面类型伪装为 iPadOS，这样可以在 iPhone 上使用所有 iPadOS 多任务功能。效果类似 TrollPad，但可能导致一些问题。\n请不要在台前调度中关闭显示 Dock，否则手机横屏时会 bootloop。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
