          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This browser is powered by vfs namecache lookups, not full directory enumeration. Some folders may appear empty unless entries are already cached. Symlinks may also be shown as files even when their targets are directories.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此浏览器基于 vfs namecache 查找，而不是完整目录枚举。除非条目已被缓存，否则某些文件夹可能显示为空。符号链接也可能在目标是目录时显示为文件。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此瀏覽器基於 vfs namecache 查找，而不是完整目錄列舉。除非項目已被快取，否則某些資料夾可能顯示為空。符號連結也可能在目標是資料夾時顯示為檔案。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This file manager is powered by vfs namecache lookups, not full directory enumeration. It may display inaccurate information.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此文件管理器基于 vfs namecache 查找，而不是完整目录枚举，可能显示不准确的信息。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "此檔案管理器基於 vfs namecache 查找，而不是完整目錄列舉，可能顯示不準確的資訊。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will delete the downloaded kernelcache and remove saved offsets.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会删除已下载的 kernelcache 并移除已保存的 offsets。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "這會刪除已下載的 kernelcache 並移除已儲存的 offsets。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will overwrite the target file with the contents of the selected source file. Target size must be >= source size.": {
      "comment": "A description of the custom overwrite process.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true,
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会用所选源文件内容覆盖目标文件。目标大小必须 >= 源文件大小。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant-TW": {
